snippet.title: Diana Roma and Oliver Have a Fun Day at the Kids Club
snippet.description:
Diana Roma and little Oliver have fun at the kids club at the Nirvana Mediterranean Excellence in Turkey. Children draw, play with toys and on the playground, in the water park, cook pizza and sweets on their own, dance and watch interesting children's shows!
Thanks for watching!
